version_description: All other versions have incorrect lyrics in certain places. This one has the correct lyrics.

This version scrolls smoothly and timely. The chords are accurately placed above or between the words where they are played. By completing the phrasing at the end of the chorus gives the soloist or duo a chance to breathe and do a good job on the break and outre. It has a definite ending for live play, doesn't 'Fade Out'.
This chord sequence seems to fit better than some of the others.
Fixes chord progressions, especially in the chorus
